com.twistral.toriamath.core.geometry.vectors

Class TVec2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.twistral.toriamath.core.geometry.vectors.TVec2

  • public class TVec2
extends java.lang.Object
    A fast and mutable 2D vector/point class.
    All methods either return a numeric value or this vector for method chaining purposes.
    Also take a look at TVec3 class for a 3D vector/point.
